Ive done some tests:

**4 methods:**
**Method 1 — leaf  (simplest, recommended starting point)**

based on provenance draft:
mpalmero@mac provenance % more source_unsigned.json 
{
  "ietf-green:sources": {
    "source": [
      {
        "id": "router-edge-01",
        "mechanisms": [ "cose-provenance" ],
        "timestamp": "2024-02-03T11:22:41Z",
